headline: GEHC Q3 Deep Dive: Margin Pressures Offset Revenue Outperformance as AI Launches Accelerate
summary: Healthcare technology company GE HealthCare Technologies (NASDAQ:GEHC) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 5.8% year on year to $5.14 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $1.07 per share was 2.2% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
